OK - This is going to sound incredibly weird but .. 

I feel like a whole person again. For the past couple months I've felt like a part of me is missing but today, while at swim practice, something happened. I was swimming and I passed like 5 people in my lane and was first and at that second I felt complete, I don't know why and I don't know how. I feel like the "old me." I feel happy and I feel complete and it's a very satisfying feeling. It feels good to find myself again ..
